667
00:34:43,780 --> 00:34:45,219
to ask the chief to let us take part in

668
00:34:45,520 --> 00:34:47,020
fire rescue operations as soon as possible?

669
00:34:47,350 --> 00:34:48,250
Yes.

670
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:49,750
Yes, Supervisor.

671
00:34:49,770 --> 00:34:50,540
No way.

672
00:34:51,060 --> 00:34:52,330
We have to follow

673
