the rules.

674
00:34:53,110 --> 00:34:54,630
You've been waiting for so long. Just wait a little longer.

675
00:34:54,659 --> 00:34:55,889
There's no need to rush.

676
00:34:56,230 --> 00:34:57,900
The rules are unreasonable.

677
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:58,380
Right.

678
00:34:58,410 --> 00:34:59,850
We are strong now.

679
00:34:59,950 --> 00:35:01,260
Then tell him yourself.

680
00:35:02,510 --> 00:35:03,550
Forget it.

681
00:35:03,590 --> 00:35:04,870
I'm afraid of being scolded.

682
00:35:05,730 --> 00:35:06,940
Is he that scary?

683
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:08,430
Yes.

684
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:09,600
Song Yan.

685
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:10,700
It's not negotiable.

686
00:35:11,570 --> 00:35:12,040
I think

687
00:35:12,090 --> 00:35:13,340
these new members

688
00:35:13,380 --> 00:35:14,660
really did well in the assessment.

689
00:35:16,830 --> 00:35:18,000
You can entrust some fire rescue missions

690
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:19,510
to them.

691
00:35:19,530 --> 00:35:20,500
And this can accelerate

692
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:22,060
the replacement of old firefighters in our station.

693
00:35:22,120 --> 00:35:23,520
A fire scene is not an amusement park.

694
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:25,790
Passing the assessment

695
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:26,860
merely means their skills have reached the standard.

696
00:35:27,380 --> 00:35:28,450
Quick reactions.

697
00:35:28,770 --> 00:35:29,820
A strong mind.

698
00:35:30,030 --> 00:35:31,070
Willpower.

699
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:32,760
They still need to practice.

700
00:35:32,930 --> 00:35:34,460
That's why they need real missions

701
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,490
to help them improve more quickly.

702
00:35:37,450 --> 00:35:38,210
They can ask me for a chance

703
00:35:38,240 --> 00:35:39,990
only after they learn

704
00:35:40,490 --> 00:35:41,330
the meaning of sacrifice.

705
00:35:41,350 --> 00:35:42,270
Sometimes, sacrifice

706
00:35:42,300 --> 00:35:43,780
can be avoided.

707
00:35:44,040 --> 00:35:46,170
With technologies nowadays,

708
00:35:46,500 --> 00:35:47,360
their safety

709
00:35:47,420 --> 00:35:48,900
can be much better protected.

710
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:51,280
In the fire in the high-rise apartment in Dongjiang,

711
00:35:52,170 --> 00:35:53,100
two firefighters lost their lives.

712
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:55,720
In the explosion that happened in the chemical factory in Ning Province,

713
00:35:56,150 --> 00:35:57,350
four firefighters lost their lives.

714
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,880
In the mountain fire in Shannan on June 25,

715
00:36:00,350 --> 00:36:01,520
17 firefighters lost their lives.

716
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:04,930
Their average age was less than 22.

717
00:36:09,670 --> 00:36:11,150
Sacrifice is not a tradition,

718
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:14,210
but it is the reality

719
00:36:15,260 --> 00:36:16,570
this team has to face.

720
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:27,750
I actually don't understand.

721
00:36:28,710 --> 00:36:30,460
With your family background,

722
00:36:31,090 --> 00:36:32,510
you can gild yourself anywhere.

723
00:36:32,970 --> 00:36:34,500
Why did you come here?

724
00:36:35,390 --> 00:36:36,540
What do you mean?

725
00:36:38,610 --> 00:36:40,130
You think I'm here to gild myself?

726
00:36:41,470 --> 00:36:43,090
What's wrong with my family background?

727
00:36:43,500 --> 00:36:44,200
Chief Song,

728
00:36:44,230 --> 00:36:46,140
this is reverse discrimination.

729
00:36:46,670 --> 00:36:47,850
Can't it be that I love this job,

730
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:48,650
like this job,

731
00:36:48,670 --> 00:36:49,310
and want to do something

732
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,420
for this job?

733
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:53,880
Yes, I know.

734
00:36:54,210 --> 00:36:56,220
It's hard for you to accept me emotionally.

735
00:36:56,260 --> 00:36:58,300
I'm here to replace Supervisor Suo.

736
00:36:59,270 --> 00:37:00,270
About many things,

737
00:37:00,790 --> 00:37:02,120
I can't empathize with you

738
00:37:02,510 --> 00:37:03,390
and share a tacit understanding with you

739
00:37:03,560 --> 00:37:04,430
like him.

740
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:08,240
But time can change it.

741
00:37:10,690 --> 00:37:11,500
I just want you to know

742
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:12,310
one thing.

743
00:37:12,770 --> 00:37:13,410
I am

744
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:16,960
not here to idle away my time.

745
00:37:40,750 --> 00:37:43,270
