764
00:38:20,810 --> 00:38:21,810
I'm not like you.

765
00:38:21,830 --> 00:38:22,910
You are locals.

766
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:25,160
If I want to stay here after graduation,

767
00:38:25,850 --> 00:38:27,290
I probably can't even afford the rent.

768
00:38:29,430 --> 00:38:31,270
Then find a rich boyfriend.

769
00:38:32,220 --> 00:38:33,570
Do you know?

770
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:35,720
Wu Qingqing from the next dorm

771
00:38:35,820 --> 00:38:37,540
found

772
00:38:37,750 --> 00:38:39,070
a boyfriend like that.

773
00:38:39,930 --> 00:38:41,100
No wonder.

774
00:38:41,150 --> 00:38:42,130
Last time, I saw her

775
00:38:42,180 --> 00:38:43,690
carrying a Chanel bag.

776
00:38:43,790 --> 00:38:45,270
