782
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:54,310
Of course we should

783
00:38:54,340 --> 00:38:55,540
make money on our own.

784
00:38:55,560 --> 00:38:56,920
Taking money from your boyfriend means nothing.

785
00:38:57,520 --> 00:38:58,920
Wait and see.

786
00:38:58,960 --> 00:38:59,870
I, Zhai Miao,

787
00:39:00,030 --> 00:39:01,820
will become a boss

788
00:39:01,860 --> 00:39:03,140
through my own efforts.

789
00:39:03,370 --> 00:39:05,180
I wish you success.

790
00:39:05,430 --> 00:39:06,470
Alright.

791
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:07,890
Let me hold the boss's hand.

792
00:39:07,930 --> 00:39:08,720
Here.

